                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980418-62-defend487 t17980418-62-punish325"></join>
               Death
            </rs>. (Aged 26.)</p>
               <p>S. Seaton, <rs id="t17980418-62-verdict326" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980418-62-verdict326" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs> (Aged 28.)</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17980418-62-punish327" type="punishmentDescription">
