                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17980418-62-defend488 t17980418-62-punish327"></join>
               Transported for fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron HOTHAM.</p>
